{"tid":1364173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"27號大家一齊入元朗共和國旅遊，振興共和國經濟","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:47.000Z","uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d7420ba74bff58cad9c7bbe027784fd6236c465","tid":1364173,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"我地組個旅行團去岩岩香港分割出黎的第一個共和團旅遊，未知會開幾多團，一團20人，<br />\n1）會帶大家睇睇水貨客最喜歡的水貨鋪<br />\n2）著名景點，元朗西鐵站同南邊圍<br />\n3）淨依幾樣景點都足夠流連忘返，歡迎拍照留念<br />\n最後請大家記得帶旅遊証件過關，關口會設在元朗西鐵站的下面巴士站，多謝合作<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iG4ZYUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiG4ZYUx.png&h=4519f019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjqqUsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjqqUsX.png&h=d4096293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76246c094cf1d290944020fd70e52eb3e432b0a6","tid":1364173,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:47.000Z","msg":"[727] 元朗好去處<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364076</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}